<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> The Member States shall carry out statistical surveys of the pig population on their territory each year with reference to one of the first days of April, August and December. </inglise>
